// Demonstrates the various kinds of infix predicate application

/- 
About: "A Person is pretty much what you would expect"
-/
STRUCTURE Person {}

GIVEN (x: Person 
       y: Person 
       z: Person)
DECIDE special
IF True

GIVEN (
    person1: Person
    person2: Person
    person3: Person
)
DECIDE eligible 
IF (person1, person2, person3) ARE special

GIVEN (person: Person)
DECIDE fun
IF True

GIVEN (x: Person)
DECIDE bleh
IF x IS fun